658        instance.setLocale(template.getLocale());
659        instance.setOrigin(template.getOrigin());
660        instance.setDeleteDaysAfterLastModification(template.getDeleteDaysAfterLastModification());
661        instance.setCustom(com.commercetools.api.models.type.CustomFieldsDraft.deepCopy(template.getCustom()));
662        return instance;
663    }
